title: DDD Melbourne
eventShortDescription:
​SSW will have 2 presenters at DDD Melbourne this year:
  • Damian Brady - Octopus Deploy and how to stop deploying like an idiot​ - 11.15am-12pm
  • ​​Ben Cull - Taking other people's money: The state of payments in Australia - 1pm-1.45pm ​
See the full DDD agenda for more details: http://www.dddmelbourne.com/agenda
